      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 is a superlative example of the E46 platform, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. Mechanically pristine, this unit has undergone comprehensive preventive maintenance, including a reinforced rear subframe and a complete VANOS overhaul to ensure peak volumetric efficiency. The 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox provides precise, short-throw shifts, delivering power to the rear wheels via a perfectly calibrated variable M differential lock. The suspension geometry remains tight with fresh bushings and original dampers that retain their factory-spec compression and rebound characteristics. With its original paint showing zero clear coat failure and an interior devoid of typical soft-touch plastic wear, this M3 is a turn-key collector-grade machine that delivers an unadulterated, analog driving experience.",
