    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional 2021 Lexus RX 350 F Sport, maintained to a standard rarely seen on the pre-owned market. The Ultra White paint retains a deep, glass-like luster, completely free of road rash, swirls, or imperfections, while the 20-inch F Sport wheels are pristine and devoid of any curb marks. Step inside to a cabin that still carries the scent of a new vehicle; the Circuit Red bolstered seats show no compression or creasing, and the perforated leather steering wheel remains matte and grippy. Every technological feature\u2014including the Mark Levinson premium audio, heads-up display, and panoramic view monitor\u2014operates with factory precision. This vehicle has been strictly garage-kept under a soft cover, never seen a drive-through car wash, and features a comprehensive, documented service history from the local Lexus dealership. For the buyer who demands perfection, this SUV delivers an authentic new-car experience.",
